message.content:
1. A statue of a wise old man holding a book, looking at it with a sense of pride and legacy.
2. A person lying on a hospital bed, surrounded by doctors and nurses, feeling dazed and amazed after surgery.
3. A young girl sitting in front of a computer, staring at the screen with a hesitant expression.
4. A person standing in the middle of a storm, feeling helpless and powerless against the strong winds.
5. A pregnant woman sitting on a couch, looking at her laptop with an impatient expression.
6. A person sitting at a table, staring at a plate of food with a regretful expression.
7. A mother sitting on a bench in a park, looking at a picture of her son with a melancholy expression.
8. A person sitting at a desk, staring at a computer screen with a doubtful expression.
9. A person driving on a highway, feeling sad and missing their hometown.
10. A person sitting in front of a computer, feeling uncomfortable and uneasy while running a program.
11. A person standing in front of a computer, feeling shocked and surprised by what they see on the screen.
12. A group of people dancing at a party, with a shy person standing in the corner watching them.
13. A person sitting on a couch, staring at a wall with a helpless and overwhelmed expression.
14. A person holding their head with a dull ache expression.
15. A person comparing two objects, feeling irritated but trying to stay realistic.
16. A pregnant woman lying on a bed, feeling lousy and uncomfortable.
17. A person sitting on a couch, feeling whiney and complaining about something.
18. A group of musicians playing on a stage, feeling happy and excited to be playing with each other.
19. A woman with long hair, trying to control her hair but feeling rebellious strands tickling her face.
20. A person standing on a scale, feeling good and proud after losing weight.
21. A person standing in front of a challenge, feeling scared and unable to be brave.
22. A family trying to entertain a bored guest, feeling frustrated and unappreciated.
23. A person sitting in a chair, feeling neurotic and anxious.
24. A person wearing a collar with a padlock, feeling submissive and obedient.
25. A person standing up for themselves, feeling empowered and strong after speaking up.
26. A person sitting in front of a TV, feeling that media content is vital for human flourishing.
27. A person feeling remorseful after an outburst, trying to make amends.
28. A teacher feeling assured that their teaching works, despite not knowing what to make of it all.
29. A person feeling thankful for a supportive work environment.
30. A person feeling helpless against a powerful enemy, resigned to their fate.
31. A person feeling unsure about changing, but not wanting to stay the same.
32. A person feeling depressed and lethargic, lacking energy and motivation.
33. A person feeling lost without their friends, who are not going on a trip with them.
34. A person feeling frustrated with their hyper-focus, unable to make progress on other tasks.
35. A person feeling damaged and unable to speak.
36. A person feeling strange and uncomfortable in a new situation, but pushing through it.
37. A person rarely feeling hesitant to speak their mind, sometimes even speaking too much.
38. A person feeling jealous and insecure in a relationship.
39. A person hoping to feel divine inspiration and motivation, but focusing on raising children for now.
40. A person feeling welcome in a new place.
41. A person feeling the negative effects of smoking, unable to enjoy life's simple pleasures.
42. A person feeling no longer disadvantaged by their ethnicity, despite the racism in the gay community.
43. A person feeling regretful for not stopping someone from smoking, wishing they could undo the damage.
44. A person feeling clever and accomplished after hauling goods to a lava planet.
45. A person feeling unhappy and only wanting to write when they feel that way.
46. A person feeling low and lonely on a grey day.
47. A person feeling the love and support of the Moxie Fab community.
48. A person feeling relief and sunshine after sharing good news.
49. A person feeling happy and melting away in a moment of joy.
50. A person feeling a longing for knowledge and seeking to learn more.
